post.description:
Stream chat responses from the SEO Advisor using Server-Sent Events (SSE).

    The advisor can:
    - Analyze your project's scan results
    - Provide actionable recommendations
    - Use tools to look up data and create tasks
    - Answer questions about SEO best practices

    **SSE Event Format:**
    ```json
    {"type": "text", "content": "..."}
    {"type": "tool_start", "tool": "...", "tool_use_id": "...", "args": {...}}
    {"type": "tool_result", "tool": "...", "tool_use_id": "...", "result": {...}}
    {"type": "done", "conversation_id": "..."}
    {"type": "error", "error": "..."}
    ```
